public abstract class AbstractEnumUserType<E extends java.lang.Enum,V extends java.io.Serializable>
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.hibernate.usertype.UserType, org.hibernate.usertype.ParameterizedType

This class represents base class for all hibernate custom user types that represent enum as some simple sql type.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Ivan Khalopik
